text: Oh, you chose the fried chicken set meal today.

Yes, since the Producer said
it was delicious yesterday...

Freshly fried, it looks juicy...
Ah, it's hot!
Oh no, are you okay!? Here, use this towel...

I'm sorry... I got carried away thinking
about my comments while eating...

Well, gourmet reporting might be a bit challenging
for me after all. My vocabulary isn't very extensive.

Hmm... While words are important,
conveying the taste isn't just about that, is it?

Hiori, you know, conveying deliciousness isn't just
about words. You have many ways to do it.
